    "title": "AI conversation persistence — DB-backed chat history that survives restarts",
    "description": "Move AI conversation history from the in-memory Map to PostgreSQL. Currently, all conversation context is lost on restart (MAX_HISTORY=20 per channel, in-memory only). With DB persistence: conversations survive restarts, history can be longer/configurable, and older context can be loaded on demand. Uses the existing pg pool from db.js. Conversation table stores messages with channel_id, role, content, and timestamp.",
