    "id": "task_20260211_Mi-Dxn",
    "title": "Persistent Logging to PostgreSQL",
    "description": "Add a PostgreSQL transport to Winston so bot logs are persisted to the database alongside file/console output.\n\n## Requirements\n- Custom Winston transport that writes log entries to a PostgreSQL table\n- Log table schema: id, level, message, metadata (JSONB), timestamp\n- Configurable via config.json (enable/disable, min log level for DB, retention days)\n- Auto-prune old logs based on retention config\n- Query endpoint or utility for viewing logs (for future dashboard integration)\n- Should not block or slow down the bot if DB is unavailable — fail gracefully\n- Respect existing log levels and structured metadata already in use\n\n## Implementation Notes\n- Use the existing db.js pool — no separate connection\n- Migration: CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS on startup\n- Consider batch inserts to reduce DB round-trips\n- Index on timestamp + level for efficient querying\n- Dashboard task (task_20260211_5MVqiX) will eventually consume these logs",
    "type": "feature",
    "status": "todo",
    "priority": "medium",
    "project": "bill-bot",
    "sprint": "sprint-1-foundation-E8UFrB",
    "created": "2026-02-11T13:53:45.193Z",
    "updated": "2026-02-11T13:53:50.203Z"
  },
  {
    "id": "task_20260211_jQslWm",
    "title": "Secret &amp; API Key Manager for Pip Build",
    "description": "Set up a centralized secret and API key management system so Pip Build (and sub-agents) can securely access credentials without hardcoding them in configs, memory files, or task descriptions.\n\n## Requirements\n- Centralized secret store accessible from the build workspace\n- Support for API keys, tokens, connection strings, OAuth credentials\n- CLI interface for get/set/list/rotate operations\n- Integration with codesession, Claude Code, and sub-agent workflows\n- Secrets never appear in logs, memory files, git history, or Discord messages\n- Rotation support with notifications when keys expire\n\n## Candidates to Evaluate\n- dotenv-vault or similar encrypted .env management\n- 1Password CLI (op) if Bill has an account\n- Bitwarden CLI\n- Custom encrypted JSON store with age/sops\n- OpenClaw native env vars (already used for some keys)\n\n## Keys to Manage\n- ANTHROPIC_API_KEY\n- OPENAI_API_KEY\n- GOOGLE_API_KEY\n- DATABASE_URL (Railway)\n- Discord bot tokens (Pip, Pip Build, bills-bot)\n- GitHub tokens\n- Twilio credentials\n- mem0 API key\n- Brave Search API key\n- Any future service credentials",
    "type": "automation",
    "status": "todo",
    "priority": "medium",
    "project": "bill-bot",
    "sprint": "sprint-1-foundation-E8UFrB",
    "created": "2026-02-11T10:57:28.415Z",
